column7: Dr. Patel focuses on congenital heart diseases in children and adolescents.
Dr. Wilson specializes in neurological disorders in children, including epilepsy and developmental delays.
Dr. Rodriguez is an expert in childhood respiratory conditions, including asthma and cystic fibrosis.
Dr. Kim provides comprehensive care for various skin conditions and dermatological diseases.
Dr. Smith specializes in aesthetic procedures and cosmetic dermatology treatments.
Dr. Johnson focuses on skin conditions affecting infants, children, and adolescents.
Dr. Chen specializes in non-invasive diagnostic techniques with expertise in echocardiography.
Dr. Johnson is a compassionate pediatrician with special interest in child development and preventive care.
Dr. Harrison is a general practitioner with experience in primary care and preventive medicine.
Dr. Smith specializes in cardiac interventions with 15 years of experience in complex cardiac procedures.
Dr. Johnson specializes in sports injuries and joint reconstruction. He has extensive experience in arthroscopic surgery and has treated professional athletes.
Dr. Garcia is an expert in spinal disorders and minimally invasive spine surgery. She focuses on treating back pain and spinal deformities.
Dr. Thompson specializes in pediatric orthopedic conditions including congenital disorders, fractures, and growth-related issues in children.
Dr. Chen is a leading expert in stroke treatment and prevention. He has published extensively on cerebrovascular disorders and acute stroke care.
Dr. Williams specializes in epilepsy management and sleep medicine. She uses advanced EEG monitoring and focuses on comprehensive epilepsy care.
Dr. Patel is a renowned retinal specialist with expertise in diabetic retinopathy, macular degeneration, and retinal detachment surgery.
Dr. Anderson specializes in advanced cataract surgery and refractive procedures including LASIK and premium intraocular lens implantation.
Dr. Kim focuses on glaucoma management and corneal transplantation. He is skilled in minimally invasive glaucoma surgery techniques.
Dr. Mitchell specializes in comprehensive family healthcare for patients of all ages.
Dr. Zhang has extensive experience in emergency care and trauma medicine.
